### Part 7: Handling the `SidebarProvider` CSS Override

The proposed `SidebarProvider` className: `"!h-full !min-h-0 flex-col overflow-hidden bg-sidebar"`.

The `SidebarProvider` internally applies: `"group/sidebar-wrapper has-data-[variant=inset]:bg-sidebar flex min-h-svh w-full"`.

The final computed classes: `group/sidebar-wrapper has-data-[variant=inset]:bg-sidebar flex min-h-svh w-full !h-full !min-h-0 flex-col overflow-hidden bg-sidebar`.

