- `min-h-svh` is overridden by `!min-h-0` (correct -- we want the provider to fill the parent, not exceed it).
- `!h-full` forces `height: 100%` to match the parent `<div class="flex flex-1 overflow-hidden">` from `(app)/layout.tsx`.

