### 3.2 Restructure `(workspace)/layout.tsx` with header-above-content

**File**: `[slug]/(workspace)/layout.tsx`

Key changes from Phase 1:
- Add `flex-col` to SidebarProvider for vertical stacking (header row + content row)
- Add two-column header: left section = sidebar-width (TeamSwitcher), right section = flex-1 (AppHeader)
- Content row wraps sidebar + inset

```tsx
return (
  <HydrateClient>
    <SidebarProvider className="!h-full !min-h-0 flex-col overflow-hidden bg-sidebar">
      {/* Header row — full width, two columns */}
      <div className="flex h-14 w-full shrink-0 items-center">
        {/* Left: matches sidebar width, desktop only */}
        <div className="hidden lg:flex w-[--sidebar-width] shrink-0 items-center justify-between px-4">
          <Suspense fallback={<div className="h-6 w-24" />}>
